<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧٣٥٠ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ الثَّوْرِيِّ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي الْهَاشِمَةِ فِي الرَّأْسِ سَمِعْنَا أَنَّ فِيهَا أَلْفَ دِرْهَمٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>